{"tid":2001382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Trump:中國採取封關措施, 但就容許民眾出境到世界各地","createTime":"2020-05-04T13:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T15:42:53.000Z","uid":75656,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7088a4237cf917c7e5be9cb4adaafcbd7cf2d6","tid":2001382,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:08:13.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普說, 中國犯下的一個可怕的錯誤, 令新冠病毒擴散.<br />\n<br />\n        特朗普接受霍士新聞節目訪問, 批評中國試圖掩飾, 隱瞞疫情, 誤導全世界和世界衛生組織,<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 在疫情爆發初期拒絕美國派員到武漢調查, 中國採取封關措施, 但就容許民眾出境到世界各地.</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n        美國國務卿蓬佩奧接受美國廣播公司訪問時說, 有大量證據證明冠狀病毒來自武漢的實驗室, 相信不是有人故意散播病毒, 但中國的流行病學實驗室安全和保安差劣, 這次也並非首次因為中國的實驗室失誤, 令病毒散播全球, 中國要為疫情負責.<br />\n<br />\n        另外, 美國國土安全部的情報文件指, 相信中國隱瞞疫情, 以及病毒的高度傳染力, 淡化病毒的嚴重性, 藉此囤積必需的醫療物資, 並嘗試隱瞞, 否認實施出口限制, 又混淆貿易數據掩飾.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20200504155555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20200504155555&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1mg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=acd1cb66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20200504155555</a>"},{"pid":"2d224d95de0427e9b18e9bf47bfb33cb3e180e3d","tid":2001382,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376b3f10cfc56972cd05c688baac152b8bd9647d","tid":2001382,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"事實"},{"pid":"b465d4f253022790469de9bd3a0d3ac017ba2c8b","tid":2001382,"uid":48040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"還有林鄭開放中國人來港，使用香港作為跳板<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC7YbpoujZlw&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1mg5